		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi,
<br />
<br />Recently I've stumbled upon a Mario Paint game, but I do not have a mouse. I'm wondering if anyone have seen the project to connect the ordinary PS/2 mouse to the SNES. 
<br />
<br />If not, I was thinking of making a PIC or Atmel based adapter, but haven't looked deep into the protocol. 
<br />
<br />Do you have any tips for me?

		

		</td>
